Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.46,0:00:16.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,故意遲到  那是以前男生的行為…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.02,0:00:36.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  久等了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.15,0:00:38.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.06,0:02:00.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天真開心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.00,0:02:02.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.45,0:02:03.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.50,0:02:05.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.03,0:03:58.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  就只差一點了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.74,0:04:00.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誠這個笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.83,0:04:07.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼聽都是誠的魯莽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.89,0:04:09.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不顧及桂同學的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.69,0:04:12.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  我可沒有這個意思…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.62,0:04:13.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.63,0:04:15.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那真怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.53,0:04:20.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  你還是多去瞭解一點女孩的心思吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.78,0:04:28.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道啊  所以…比如…之前…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.99,0:04:35.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨  笨蛋  考慮一下對象啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.36,0:04:37.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和誠是朋友  你明白嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.99,0:04:39.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.43,0:04:41.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以那就像是打招呼一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.13,0:04:44.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誠你向桂同學索吻是認真的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.95,0:04:48.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  打招呼？這裏可是日本啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.36,0:04:50.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之  下次給我好好幹
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.68,0:04:52.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.24,0:04:54.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好  那就把這個給你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.86,0:04:57.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.92,0:04:59.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電影票
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.10,0:05:02.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次一定要讓桂同學高興起來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.06,0:05:04.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進展順利的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.14,0:05:06.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進展順利的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.50,0:05:09.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在絕妙的氣氛下  兩人在黑暗中…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.41,0:05:11.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很自然地兩人握住雙手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.46,0:05:16.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩人的視線不是看著銀幕而是互相凝視
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.67,0:05:17.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.77,0:05:18.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.49,0:05:19.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啾～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.55,0:05:22.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  真  真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.92,0:05:24.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.40,0:05:27.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.98,0:05:31.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誠真像個孩子  讓人頭疼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.14,0:05:34.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界  那票是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.33,0:05:35.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  想去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.10,0:05:37.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是約伊藤去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.54,0:05:50.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可沒這麼閒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.94,0:06:03.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電影嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.67,0:06:05.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次約會者超級常見的傳統項目
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.21,0:06:10.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在浪漫的氣氛中提高女友的期待值
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.95,0:06:13.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼這次一定要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.74,0:06:16.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接…接吻…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.88,0:06:23.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從哪個角度親才是關鍵呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.56,0:06:25.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彎下腰比較好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.67,0:06:28.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過踮起腳的桂同學也很誘人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.94,0:06:32.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不  不  我可萬萬不能操之過急
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.57,0:06:35.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先要這樣  緊抱在一起  握手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.75,0:06:38.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  反了吧  不是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.73,0:06:40.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  刷個牙  換新的內褲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.87,0:06:42.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指甲也要剪下比較好…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.37,0:06:45.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這票到明天不就截止了嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.68,0:07:02.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊藤同學…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.34,0:07:08.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交往  這樣就是這樣的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.89,0:07:11.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐  手機響了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.14,0:07:12.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.36,0:07:28.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以看你喜歡的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.49,0:07:30.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要看哪個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.81,0:07:32.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.46,0:07:38.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  伊藤同學  我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.40,0:07:42.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  只有這個了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.62,0:07:54.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾米麗婭很害怕嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.18,0:07:56.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼特欺負人家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.16,0:08:00.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨  打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.39,0:08:01.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  克莉斯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.09,0:08:05.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然說到約會  還是要看愛情故事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.19,0:08:14.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你  克莉斯  把彼特介紹給我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.00,0:08:17.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油  那傢伙雖然很糊塗不過是個好人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.87,0:08:20.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…  不過克莉斯  其實…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.06,0:08:23.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別在意  別在意  晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.08,0:08:28.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得  很像我們啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.25,0:08:33.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克莉斯是西園寺同學  艾米麗婭是我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.10,0:08:35.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  我是彼特？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.95,0:08:36.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.91,0:08:39.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣說的話  人際關係倒是挺像的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.93,0:08:44.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  雖然是感覺  演彼特的那演員好像跟伊藤同學很像
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.84,0:08:48.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點帥…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.31,0:08:50.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.16,0:08:54.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過艾米麗婭跟桂不像呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.66,0:08:55.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.91,0:09:01.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  比起艾米麗婭  桂更加可愛呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.33,0:09:08.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼特  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.92,0:09:10.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都不用說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.41,0:09:11.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼特…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.96,0:09:16.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然很可愛啊  桂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.17,0:09:19.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  今天一定要成功
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.03,0:09:42.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把燈關了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.58,0:09:48.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桂的手指好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.89,0:09:52.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在絕妙的氣氛下  兩人在黑暗中…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.88,0:09:58.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很自然地兩人握住雙手  兩人的視線不是看著銀幕而是互相凝視
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.13,0:10:00.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.27,0:10:00.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.12,0:10:03.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啾～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.10,0:10:04.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾米麗婭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.03,0:10:07.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…不…  彼特  那裏是胸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.86,0:10:09.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮啊  艾米麗婭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.97,0:10:11.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀  好害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.91,0:10:12.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是不願意的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.79,0:10:15.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不要欺負人家
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.79,0:10:18.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桂的胸部好大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.90,0:10:23.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊  世界不是說過嗎  桂只是在害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.59,0:10:25.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實際是在等我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.50,0:10:28.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  桂  我沒意識到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.58,0:10:31.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  現在…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.08,0:10:35.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮  桂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.82,0:10:37.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好溫暖
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.99,0:10:39.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  那個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.74,0:10:41.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  手…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.43,0:10:45.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,握住手了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.41,0:10:48.37,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}不行了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.15,0:10:51.10,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}現在就是決定性的一擊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.26,0:10:53.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桂  吻你的嘴唇…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.91,0:10:54.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.32,0:11:08.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不知道嗎  我和彼特在交往
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.97,0:11:09.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.99,0:11:14.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見了  艾米麗婭  我們就算畢業  也可以做朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.22,0:11:16.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克莉斯…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.42,0:11:22.47,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙臉紅  真噁心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.75,0:11:23.82,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪個哪個
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.82,0:11:25.78,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像給壓扁的青蛙一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.90,0:11:26.90,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常同意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.09,0:11:30.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  是世界…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.42,0:11:32.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西園寺同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.54,0:11:37.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼說呢  那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.83,0:11:40.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說桂也只是在害羞什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.14,0:11:45.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實際上  電影票也是世界給我的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.57,0:11:47.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個多管閒事的傢伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.34,0:11:49.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊藤同學你…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.40,0:11:55.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊藤同學跟西園寺同學  那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.25,0:11:59.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關係真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.56,0:12:01.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還好  是同桌嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.85,0:12:28.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一站是  原巳濱  原巳濱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.07,0:12:31.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  我下車了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.71,0:12:36.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.84,0:12:40.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.89,0:12:43.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  桂？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.00,0:12:58.00,STAFF,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,0)\pos(275,96)\bord1\fs16\fscy90\fscx110}SumiSora&CASO
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.21,0:13:07.11,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}化學反應有像火藥爆炸一樣  瞬間就完成的快速反應
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.31,0:13:10.83,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}也有像鐵生銹一樣的很慢的反應
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.26,0:13:05.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  到底怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.45,0:13:09.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我完全按你說的做了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.79,0:13:11.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誠是大笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.51,0:13:13.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後面  太吵了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.04,0:13:15.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.51,0:13:18.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們倆看起來很和諧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.32,0:13:25.63,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}現在來講關於改變反應速度的條件
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.55,0:13:25.18,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}聲音太大了  笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.33,0:13:28.22,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}笨蛋  笨蛋  笨蛋  笨蛋  笨蛋…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.24,0:13:32.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.29,0:13:33.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底誰才是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.20,0:13:40.20,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}那之後和好了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.63,0:13:42.20,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}還沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.72,0:13:53.75,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}我不知道桂是怎麼想的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.95,0:13:56.25,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}大概是還不習慣男孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.89,0:13:57.85,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}是這問題嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.50,0:13:58.99,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}嗯  她只是嚇了一跳而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.29,0:14:01.77,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}誠太猴急了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.01,0:14:07.85,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}因為桂同學是很敏感的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.58,0:14:11.12,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}但書上寫的是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.30,0:14:14.08,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}書？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.35,0:14:14.08,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}試著買了本戀愛指導書
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.34,0:14:15.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是笨蛋嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.76,0:14:17.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才是笨蛋  西園寺
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.10,0:14:19.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對…對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.62,0:14:22.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼只罵我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.17,0:14:23.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.60,0:14:32.18,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}反正先去好好道歉  和好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.45,0:14:34.18,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}我是想那樣做可…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.73,0:14:37.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有看那些書的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.75,0:14:40.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不如好好努力去瞭解下現實中的桂同學啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.72,0:14:42.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是喜歡桂同學嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.73,0:14:48.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.98,0:14:54.61,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}加油  男孩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.71,0:15:08.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  伊藤？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.40,0:15:10.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加藤
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.45,0:15:14.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  來我們的教室  很難得啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.08,0:15:17.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來這裏找個熟人  有點事…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.34,0:15:18.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰？我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.10,0:15:20.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要特意來找你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.08,0:15:22.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是和以前一樣很沒禮貌呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.19,0:15:25.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是誰？我幫你叫他來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.04,0:15:29.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桂  桂言葉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.29,0:15:33.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊藤和她是朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.61,0:15:35.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是…吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.60,0:15:37.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桂呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.08,0:15:40.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那她對你說過什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.98,0:15:41.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.95,0:15:43.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一副很消沉的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.66,0:15:46.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是你的錯覺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.45,0:15:48.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話我幫你處理吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.55,0:15:49.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.52,0:15:52.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看在同是一所中學的情面上  會算你便宜點哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.09,0:15:54.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我說了  不是那麼回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.96,0:15:56.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕  再見
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.66,0:15:58.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加藤
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.65,0:16:05.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在急著幹什麼啊  今天有什麼事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.00,0:16:06.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很重要的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.99,0:16:08.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？和我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.94,0:16:09.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.33,0:16:13.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺那傢伙最近很難相處啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.92,0:16:17.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次一定要…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.89,0:16:20.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.53,0:16:24.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能稍微聊下嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.43,0:16:28.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  我還有委員會要開…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.68,0:16:29.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結束後呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.00,0:16:31.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很晚才能結束
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.46,0:16:32.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會等的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.46,0:16:33.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  回家有規定的時間…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.95,0:16:36.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點  一點時間就夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.55,0:16:40.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會再做那種事了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.00,0:16:46.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到會惹你那麼反感
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.83,0:16:50.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要牽你的手是事實
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.43,0:16:54.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老實說接著的事也想了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.53,0:16:58.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這些的出發點不是想惹桂討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.75,0:17:00.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一點我希望你可以理解
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.31,0:17:03.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  想重新來過
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.42,0:17:07.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  還想知道更多桂的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.15,0:17:09.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.06,0:17:12.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,委員會要開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.48,0:17:18.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在車站  月台等你  一直等你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.30,0:17:40.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在回家嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.32,0:17:41.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.77,0:17:44.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,車站不在這邊哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.34,0:17:47.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今  今天坐公車…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.46,0:17:49.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼  一直都是坐電車吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.07,0:17:52.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶爾也坐下公車
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.84,0:17:54.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想坐電車嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.72,0:17:57.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.61,0:18:00.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是今天想坐公車而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.11,0:18:01.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為誠在車站？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.89,0:18:16.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為那傢伙是個笨蛋  所以一定在等你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.98,0:18:24.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經討厭他了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.61,0:18:28.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是的話  不當面說的話他是不會懂的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.01,0:18:30.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為他是個笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.52,0:18:32.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別老是笨蛋笨蛋的說個不停
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.05,0:18:34.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊藤同學不是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.18,0:18:37.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是稍微積極了點…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.23,0:18:48.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  兩個都是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.72,0:18:56.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把你所想的原原本本地告訴他不就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.65,0:19:03.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？  真要把這個送給我？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.37,0:19:05.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的行嗎？  不會還你了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.44,0:19:07.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過那書完全沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.48,0:19:10.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並不是討厭他呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.71,0:19:14.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.81,0:19:15.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.85,0:19:17.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男孩子們全都…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.77,0:19:25.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從小學高年級開始胸部就是班上最大的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.69,0:19:26.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.41,0:19:30.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此常常被耍  被欺負
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.09,0:19:33.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那和誠所做的完全不一樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.88,0:19:36.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道  我雖然知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.86,0:19:38.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶  桂同學
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.40,0:19:43.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誠是非常想好好珍惜桂同學的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.41,0:19:45.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那樣嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.67,0:19:49.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧  首先桂同學連這點就沒注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.03,0:19:56.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但只是誠單方面有這意思的話  一定持續不了多久
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.04,0:20:00.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桂同學有考慮過誠的心情嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.61,0:20:03.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「想做些什麼呢」等等
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.04,0:20:07.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  男女交往不就是這回事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.62,0:20:07.27,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}伊藤？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.72,0:20:09.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感情的共有什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.57,0:20:10.63,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}一起回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.57,0:20:12.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男朋友  女朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.95,0:20:17.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且只會想那些H事情的誠
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.91,0:20:19.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只做了現在這些舉動  已經很壓抑自己了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.93,0:20:22.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？H的事情嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.97,0:20:25.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男孩子的話  那算是很普通的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.95,0:20:28.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想他已經很努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.44,0:20:30.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  是那樣嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.61,0:20:31.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.79,0:20:32.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,換成其他人的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.06,0:20:34.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定立刻就像這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.75,0:20:40.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的  讓給誠太浪費了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.54,0:20:39.93,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}西  西園寺同學
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.23,0:20:41.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難怪他那麼想了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.26,0:20:42.71,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}不要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.00,0:20:46.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  閒事就管到這裏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.91,0:20:49.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西園寺同學
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.31,0:20:49.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.53,0:20:54.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西園寺同學真的是很瞭解伊藤同學呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.75,0:20:55.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.51,0:20:56.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真讓人羨慕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.30,0:20:59.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒  沒那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.64,0:21:03.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是同桌  在一起的時間長了一點而已
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.42,0:21:05.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.66,0:21:08.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微多細心留意下他
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.43,0:21:11.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話一定能理解的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.73,0:21:15.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  其實西園寺同學對伊藤同學…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.82,0:21:17.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  到底怎麼樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.33,0:21:34.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要走了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.23,0:21:37.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公車？還是電車？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.49,0:21:50.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.52,0:21:56.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  我還以為你不來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.24,0:22:00.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…  我相信你一定會來的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.64,0:22:01.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼說呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.32,0:22:05.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桂
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.26,0:22:11.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我發誓絕對不會再做惹桂不高興的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.50,0:22:12.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.66,0:22:17.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我更想進一步瞭解伊藤同學
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.39,0:22:24.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我  會努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.98,0:22:56.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我是伊藤同學的女朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.16,0:22:58.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要更加瞭解你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.78,0:23:01.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
